<view class="page">
  <view class="page-title">拍照识别</view>
  <view class="subtitle">我会先猜可能的食材。选中后会进入添加页，你可以再确认日期、保存方式和宝宝建议。</view>

  <view class="camera-card">
    <view class="camera-frame" bindtap="chooseImage">
      <image wx:if="{{hasImage}}" class="preview-image" src="{{imagePath}}" mode="aspectFill" />
      <block wx:else>
        <image class="camera-icon" src="{{assets.actions.camera}}" mode="aspectFit" />
        <view class="camera-text">拍照或从相册选择</view>
      </block>
      <view class="corner lt"></view>
      <view class="corner rt"></view>
      <view class="corner lb"></view>
      <view class="corner rb"></view>
    </view>
    <view class="recognize-state">
      <image class="tiny-baby" src="{{assets.mascot.babyHappy}}" mode="aspectFit" />
      <text>{{recognizing ? '识别中...' : '识别结果仅供参考，请以实际为准'}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="paper-card" wx:if="{{results.length}}">
    <view class="section-title">识别结果（请选择一个）</view>
    <view class="result-helper">识别不一定准确，请点最接近的食材。选中后可确认保存日期和方式。</view>
    <view class="result-card" wx:for="{{results}}" wx:key="foodId" data-id="{{item.foodId}}" bindtap="chooseResult">
      <image class="result-icon" src="{{item.icon}}" mode="aspectFit" />
      <view class="result-main">
        <view class="result-label">可能是</view>
        <view class="result-name">{{item.foodName}}</view>
        <view class="confidence-bar"><view class="confidence-fill" style="width: {{item.percent}}%;"></view></view>
        <view class="confidence-copy">识别把握：{{item.percent}}%</view>
      </view>
      <view class="result-action">添加</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="pixel-btn secondary manual-btn" bindtap="manualSearch">手动搜索</view>
  <view class="disclaimer">不要把识别结果视为准确判断。如果没有合适结果，请用手动搜索。</view>
</view>
